1. Transparency & Privacy:
   This software is NOT intended to steal, exfiltrate, or misuse any private
   or sensitive information from your servers. Its sole purpose is to
   collect operational metrics (CPU, memory, storage, processes, network, etc.)
   in order to help DevOps and system administrators monitor and track
   the health of their infrastructure.

2. Intended Use:
   This agent is designed for monitoring multiple servers, whether on-premises
   or in the cloud, providing visibility into system performance and resource
   utilization across environments.

